document.full_text: albania's mayoral elections, seen as a key test for the country in its campaign for eu membership, were competitive and transparent but marred by political wrangling and mistrust, international observers said tuesday.
document.title: albania vote competitive say international observers
lines_and_colors: albania's mayoral elections, seen as a key test for the country in its campaign for eu membership, were competitive and transparent but marred by political wrangling and mistrust, international observers said tuesday.
